{
  "stem": "5103.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And her name-- she asked me my name, was Corrie-- and her name was Carey.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Her name was with an A.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was very unusual, because Carey and Corrie.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said, oh, I've got the two Cs, you know, in my home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't understand what she meant by the, like, initials.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What did I know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't read yet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- but I remember her telling me this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said, now we're going to have something to eat, and you've had a long trip.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know how long the trip took.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I really couldn't tell you, from Amsterdam to Rotterdam, how long it took.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] she said, go and have something, and have a look where you're going to sleep.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a little room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I looked in the room, and there were two beds, like bunk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I slept down, and Carey was going to sleep up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was lonely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I felt I missed my mommy and dad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I, I felt sad, but I was also happy that I had a little friend.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So you know-- then after a little while, Carey told me, this is your little place where you're going to be, and all this.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I-- she was also a Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She had big brown eyes and red hair, real frizzy red hair.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she was about my height.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When you're a child, you don't take notice of this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She was my contemporary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then when we came into the lounge room, there was only Anna there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH] had gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I felt like my whole world had collapsed, because this man, to me, was going to take my mother and father's place, and now he'd gone.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
